Task: Add bounded latest-history prefetch and recent previews

Summary:
- Reduced initial channel history pages to a 30-message latest preview while keeping thread history at 50.
- Limited cached first renders to the latest preview page.
- Added bounded background prefetch for likely channel histories after conversation refresh, skipping already cached histories and avoiding read-state changes.
- Added unit coverage for cached previews and prefetch candidate ranking/bounding.

Modified files:
- src/slack.rs
- src/runtime.rs
- conductor/tracks.md
- conductor/tracks/instant_channel_loading_20260707/spec.md
